<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV52">
<l>aḻaikkuṅ karuṅkaṭal veṇṭiraik kaikoṇṭu pōyalarvāy</l>
<l>maḻaikkaṇ maṭantai yaravaṇai yēṟamaṇ mātarviṇvā</l>
<l>yaḻaittup pulampi mulaimalai mēṉiṉṟu māṟukaḷāy</l>
<l>maḻaikkaṇṇa nīrtiru mālkoṭi yāṉeṉṟu vārkiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When, as the white waves of the beckoning black sea took  [her] by the hand,</l>
<l>the rain-eyed girl from the bloosom rises onto the serpent bed, the earth woman’s</l>
<l>heavenly mouth cries in loneliness [and] the water from [her] rain eyes</l>
<l>constantly flows on [her] breast mountains as rivers: “Tirumāl is cruel”.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
